  <p>Vox Media is one of the fastest-growing online publishers, focused on lifestyle brands that connect with passionate audiences. </p>
  <p>Vox Media creates things for the internet…but didn't represent itself anywhere. Because most revenue is brought in by ads, we needed a place to centralize advertising information so that companies could better approach us. We needed to focus on showing our brands, their audiences, different ad units, all while maintaining a unified feel.</p>

